SchildiChat Web/Desktop is a fork of Element [Web](https://github.com/vector-im/element-web)/[Desktop](https://github.com/vector-im/element-desktop).

The most important changes of SchildiChat compared to Element are:
- A unified chat list for both direct and group chats
- Message bubbles
- Bigger items in the room list
- &hellip; and more!

**Discussion**: [#web:schildi.chat](https://matrix.to/#/#web:schildi.chat)  
